---
// Landing page for the Pokédex application
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Pokédex</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body { font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif; background: #ffffff; color: #1a1a1a; min-height: 100vh; }
      nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
      nav a { color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 2rem; opacity: 0.6; transition: opacity 0.2s; font-weight: 600; }
      nav a:hover { opacity: 1; }
      .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #f97316; }
      hero { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; padding: 6rem 2rem; gap: 1.5rem; }
      h1 { font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; }
      h1 span { color: #f97316; }
      p { font-size: 1.25rem; opacity: 0.5; max-width: 480px; }
      .btn { background: #f97316; color: white; padding: 0.875rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 1rem; transition: background 0.2s; }
      .btn:hover { background: #ea6c00; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <span class="logo">Pokédex</span>
      <div>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/pokedex">Pokédex</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <hero>
      <h1>Explore the<br /><span>Pokémon</span> World</h1>
      <p>Browse the complete Pokédex, discover stats, abilities, and types for every Pokémon.</p>
      <a href="/pokedex" class="btn">Open Pokédex</a>
    </hero>
  </body>
</html>